{"id":313032,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-浙江维权律师庄道鹤被以涉嫌颠覆罪/","date":"2013-09-11T16:49:23Z","modified":"2013-09-11T16:49:23Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江维权律师庄道鹤被以“涉嫌颠覆罪”传唤（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员柳青青报道）浙江大学教师、独立学者、维权律师庄道鹤于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日被杭州市公安局国保和西湖区国保以涉嫌“颠覆国家政权罪”刑事传唤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，当天下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，庄道鹤律师被警察带到杭州市公安局西湖分局西溪派出所</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号审讯室，坐在带木枷锁的犯人椅子上接受审讯。审讯室的门上方写着“坦白从宽，抗拒从严”八个大字，脚下和审讯台背面写着“说吧！早说早轻松”八个字符。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>审讯从下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点开始到晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点结束，整整审问了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>个小时。审问的主要内容有：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、与许志永和新公民运动的关系；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>要求公布官员财产的目的、意图和背景；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、与浙江民主党人及杭州的其他圈子有什么样的关系和有哪些活动；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、是否频繁地与外地的“敏感人士”接触。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zWGdG1Kjs04/UjB193mhQXI/AAAAAAAAoIg/utQZON70c-s/s1600/img383.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zWGdG1Kjs04/UjB193mhQXI/AAAAAAAAoIg/utQZON70c-s/s320/img383.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input typ